                                            <p>Your English Teacher aims to touch the lives of million and wants to keep the flame of education burning. Our objective is to lead the online education industry and be an emerging leader in the vertical of Life learning for youths. In immigration industry, we aim to serve the purpose of genuine consultancy and want to progress further as a single point of contact for all education abroad needs.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="card ">
                                    <div class="card-header " id="headingTwo">
                                        <h3 class="acdn-title collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">Our Mission
                                        </h3>
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordion">
                                        <div class="card-body">
                                            <p>We do not consider ourselves a mere training center but aims to empower generations through Trainings and Education. As Mahatma Gandhi once said, “Education is the most powerful weapon to change the world”. We aim to deliver genuine content through our trainings and workshop and spread the flame of education to each and every one.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
